I ordered delivery from this place today because the plus about their delivery is if you live in an apartment building they will come to your apartment. You don't have to come to the front of the building. I ordered cheese pizza and garlic knots. In the past, I have had their garlic knots and they were really good. But today they were totally different. They didn't even taste garlicy. They just looked like mini rolls that didn't even seem really cooked with some butter brushed over them. I was really disappointed. Also the pizza didn't taste very good. Worst pizza I have had in a long time. The crust was very bland, tasteless and tough. It tasted kind of like cardboard. I really didn't enjoy the pizza. I was very disappointed in my order. It seems the quality of their products has really gone down. Also the guy who took my order over the phone wasn't the most polite person in the world and was kind of abrupt. He got upset cause I didn't have my credit card out ready when I called. It took me about 10 seconds to get it from my wallet.
